column5: Hit Lake Ontario today with Noofy to see if the Kings were around yet …we fished 220fow to 6 fow marked a few fish deep but didn’t have the riggers on the boat to get down to 100+ ft had a good hit in 130 but lost it …water needs to warm up a tad more for the Kings ..water was 38.6 out deep and 44 was the warmest we found in close 6 fow ….it was a nice flat day to be out searching for the Silvers ..even know we didn’t manage any Silvers we found a Brown and a thing with lips snaged in the back ..Nice Brown Noofy ..lol Thanks for joining me today …    Thougth I was fishing with Sonny  lol..fish with lips
Nice brown WTG looks like a beautiful day out there  Rob
lol,,,,see it's not me it's you!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
No Carp for me Sonny Boy ..
